{"tid":148053,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[親身感受] 係東京講中文會比日本人歧視","createTime":"2017-03-08T10:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T06:14:35.000Z","uid":14170,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45885ec02d59b481284ab569162918e65f16b756","tid":148053,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:06:32.000Z","msg":"話說我 2016 年 3 - 7 月去左東京既大學交換，係當地叫做住左一段時間，唔長唔短但係睇到日本人尤其是東京人特別串 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n情境 1 : <br />\n有一次放學搭三田線返宿舍，咁啱同個台灣同學一齊搭車，一邊搭一邊細聲傾計，途中有見到有唔止一個日本人睥 / 斜視我地，好似覺得我地嘈住佢，睇唔地我地咁既眼神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我自問份人幾循規蹈矩，講野聲浪只細不大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：車上有日本學生以更大聲量傾計<br />\n<br />\n情境 2:<br />\n另一次同個新加坡同學走，亞洲人樣但全程講英文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係香港人自稱識英文個隻甩甩 cut cut 咁單詞式英文，流暢程度比得上個坡仔 (NUS) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我直接係架 peak hour 既列車度，同個新加坡仔講上次我講中文比人睥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後叫佢周圍望下啲日本上班族，今次見到佢地竟然避我視線，然後繼續傾計佢地又有意無意望過黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似對我地好好奇咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家係新宿買野或者係銀行搞户口，已經有好多識普通話既人，每次佢聽唔明我講英文，都會叫講普通話既人黎同我講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是我扮唔識普通話，逼佢搵個大粒野出黎用英文招呼我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係我港人心態，而係講普通話真係會比人歧視，搞好多手續都麻煩好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dfb6d577a94aa7bba29084cd64088057a6d3c5","tid":148053,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"自卑先會覺得人地成日歧視你，我都係東京留學緊，唔覺有乜特別"},{"pid":"f90a92df4c1d027155522dbd31450a878716007f","tid":148053,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:38:15.000Z","msg":"唔覺<br />\n反而係受歡迎"},{"pid":"e6ade2e5e1a69f3f99ab182ce2d0de56255e6cda","tid":148053,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:55:00.000Z","msg":"點解唔講日文?"},{"pid":"4bbf378e075b88be1029851ea11bc67af550495d","tid":148053,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自卑先會覺得人地成日歧視你，我都係東京留學緊，唔覺有乜特別</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你平時講咩語言"},{"pid":"67f03b0d13a0ca802df1264b04f30d9f0a36b5a2","tid":148053,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔講日文?</blockquote><br />\n唔識 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我剩係去慶應 Exchange 咋"},{"pid":"4b71672da4cde4d00ecae6feb91228b0219ebc33","tid":148053,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔覺<br />\n反而係受歡迎</blockquote><br />\n自欺欺人"},{"pid":"2235c975a879d22e54c78b6f0336760120c6bbd9","tid":148053,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}